## ðŸ“‹ **Summary**

| Aspect | Status | Finding |
|--------|--------|---------|
| **Data Source** | âœ… Verified | OKX API `/public/funding-rate-history` |
| **Data Integrity** | âœ… Correct | `fundingTime` = settlement timestamp |
| **Resampling Logic** | âœ… Correct | 8-hour alignment to settlements |
| **Selection Logic** | âŒ **BIASED** | Uses same-period rates (look-ahead) |
| **Return Application** | âŒ **BIASED** | Applies returns from ended period |
| **Overall Verdict** | âš ï¸ **INVALID** | Backtest has look-ahead bias |

**Recommended Action:** Rebuild backtest with T-1 lag enforcement before production deployment.
